text: Mia Hermansson (born 12 December 1992) is a Swedish judoka. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the 63 kg division, and was eliminated in the first round by Edwige Gwend. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Sweden Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:European Games competitors for Sweden Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games
